WEBVTT

00:05.880 --> 00:07.040
You've done well,
Numidian.

00:07.080 --> 00:09.000
There's one more thing
I want you to do.

00:09.040 --> 00:11.240
I am Vitus Aurelius,

00:11.280 --> 00:12.640
optio of the Eighth Legion.

00:12.680 --> 00:14.960
Fuck off back to Rome!

00:15.000 --> 00:16.440
Now it's a war.

00:16.480 --> 00:19.560
Yesterday, I sent an envoy
to parley with your father.

00:19.600 --> 00:21.000
Did he change his mind?

00:21.040 --> 00:22.120
Does he even know you're here?

00:22.160 --> 00:26.120
Stop killing my people.
Then I'll talk.

00:26.160 --> 00:27.320
The Regni will
accept you here,

00:27.360 --> 00:29.640
but only as allies
against the Cantii scum.

00:29.680 --> 00:32.000
You trust the Regni?

00:32.040 --> 00:33.840
Hatred
is far more reliable.

00:33.880 --> 00:35.480
Camp here.

00:35.520 --> 00:37.360
If I'm not back by sunrise,
you join the others.

00:37.400 --> 00:38.160
You understand?

00:38.200 --> 00:39.320
Yes, sir.

00:39.360 --> 00:41.520
Fuck me.

00:41.560 --> 00:43.560
Dad wasn't at home.

00:43.600 --> 00:45.240
He could have been
taken prisoner.

00:45.280 --> 00:46.480
Your dad's dead.

00:46.520 --> 00:47.720
I saw him get killed.

00:47.760 --> 00:48.920
You lying bastard!

00:48.960 --> 00:50.000
All right, I made it up.

00:50.040 --> 00:53.040
I'll find the fucking Romans
myself!

00:53.080 --> 00:55.600
You have been warned,
Aulus Plautius!

00:55.640 --> 00:57.200
Make amends!

00:59.240 --> 01:00.880
Are you sure
you're ready, Rome?

01:00.920 --> 01:03.560
Ready for what you'll find?

01:03.600 --> 01:05.239
I'm ready.

01:06.160 --> 01:08.240
Then let's begin.

01:10.000 --> 01:16.074
Advertise your product or brand here
